# Project: Gamified Habit Tracker (offline-first PWA)

A minimalist habit tracker that gamifies a healthy lifestyle. The website and the
installable phone app are ONE codebase: a static site + web app manifest + service
worker (a PWA).

## Non-negotiable principles

- Offline-first: the app must work with no network after first load.
- On-device only: all data persists to `localStorage`; nothing is sent to a server.
- No backend, no database, no auth, no accounts.
- Static and free to host. Minimalist UI, few dependencies.

## Where the truth lives

- Human overview: `docs/human/overview.md`
- Technical architecture, stack, data model, gamification: `docs/ai/architecture.md`

Read `docs/ai/architecture.md` before making structural changes.

## Scope guardrails (for now)

- No cross-device sync, social features, or notifications unless explicitly requested.
- Keep new dependencies minimal and free/static-host compatible.
